cs.HC, cs.CY, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.LG 

The paper focuses on designing an interactive interface to help stakeholders understand and manage algorithmic trade-offs, which involves human-computer interaction (cs.HC), cybersecurity and privacy (cs.CY), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper evaluates the interface on the problem of predicting criminal defendants' likelihood to re-offend, which involves criminal justice (cs.CR).
